data.description: River Forest Manor's 2 story Contemporary Home w/ Cedar Shaker Roof. Charming character throughout. Very detailed entry. Large Livingroom w/ wood-burning fireplace. Detailed Cove Ceilings. Hardwood Floors. Large Formal Dining Room. Custom Kitchen w/ loads of cabinets, granite counters. Updated half-bath. Great Room features fireplace and Huge Bay Windows. Imported tile floor. Spacious Primary Bedroom and European Marble style Bath. Full, finished Basement. Roof is decorative-solid underneath. Home is situated on an oversized lot on a desirable street.
